     35          /***************************************************************************//**
     36           * @addtogroup letimer LETIMER - Low Energy Timer
     37           * @brief Low Energy Timer (LETIMER) Peripheral API
     38           * @details
     39           *  This module contains functions to control the LETIMER peripheral of Silicon
     40           *  Labs 32-bit MCUs and SoCs. The LETIMER is a down-counter that can keep track
     41           *  of time and output configurable waveforms.
     42           * @{
     43           ******************************************************************************/
     44          
